des: Are you interested in learning fun facts about your own species? This Alexa skill helps you do just that! Ask Alexa using sample phrases such as, "Alexa, ask human facts to tell me a human fact." or "Alexa, ask human facts to give me a human trivia." Impress your friends with fun facts about us!
